Model.Game

Class PutMove

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Game.Move
      • Model.Game.PutMove

  • public class PutMove
extends Move
    This class is created when a move is made on the field (a PutMove). A PutMove is a map of Locations to Tiles with fields that hold information about the PutMove and methods to get or modify that information. Created by Martijn on 13-1-2016.
